I've been told I'm pretty good looking, so I don't mind exploring a career in acting or modelling (or just working in media).
If that doesn't work out, I guess I can fall back on muy studies. I hope to study accounting in Australia.
I keep my turban and beard and wear the steel bangle or kara, because that's just how I was raised. 
One of my best friends is Zhihao, my neighbor from a few blocks away. He can be a dumbass, but he's been there for me when times were tough.
I am in a serious relationship with Selinder. I met her on the first day of Business Economics in poly, and we've been dating since then. She's purrty, hehe.
